{"tid":810162,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人比錢百蚊食野當自己係皇帝","createTime":"2018-09-07T17:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T17:41:37.000Z","uid":38806,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f9769e88f4e5249e63c5c8bb9a3d876b45885478","tid":810162,"uid":38806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:14:54.000Z","msg":"香港人又幾有文化啊？<br />\n有一半人都係比個幾百蚊食野就當自己皇帝<br />\n唔Book位就想一黎到就有得食<br />\n大佬你諗下你自己幾多個人黎食野先啦<br />\n咁大張檯<br />\n你覺得人地拍住烏蠅等你啊？<br />\n冇得食就黑哂口臉<br />\n一係就Book個陣又唔講想坐邊<br />\n黎到又厭比個位唔好<br />\n閪哂口閪哂面<br />\nBook完又唔黎<br />\n打電話又唔聽<br />\n跟本同大陸人真係冇乜分別<br />\n都係差唔多on9姐<br />\n甚至係更on9<br />\n已經夠鐘收鋪先叫你班人埋單<br />\n都仲係到死坐爛坐<br />\n咁鐘意坐咪去M記囉<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">阻人收工正仆街！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7b920a676bfe2de4065ee30983c12b0a11265e36","tid":810162,"uid":195904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"94狂"},{"pid":"278b31a05ff8677cea55937910b26928a3f61f9c","tid":810162,"uid":60140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:16:40.000Z","msg":"哦"},{"pid":"e53dae0516099d32dc22f3e943664bb79d2a0452","tid":810162,"uid":54566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"666"},{"pid":"c6d5ca3f438f753aca5146de1475e26148c0c395","tid":810162,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:18:15.000Z","msg":"Skr"},{"pid":"00af42612e60f4427958c8479ec57fc604c1c146","tid":810162,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:22:10.000Z","msg":"牛逼"},{"pid":"f89d33904b6c373b29abfdac454861f064d13990","tid":810162,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T17:34:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cc51a94a00f9d4565109237a30fafeb06c78582d","tid":810162,"uid":38806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f89d33904b6c373b29abfdac454861f064d13990","tid":810162,"u